children.customDisplayName: What brings you here, young man?
Marlo sent me to fix your furniture
Two stools, two tables, a chair, and a rotten carpet. A bed too.
Ah, Young man, How's the redecoration coming on?
I've finished removing all the old furniture
I used to be a carpenter myself...
Some basic wooden planks and nails should do,
I'll want a new carpet too.
Do you want some planks son?
